###############################################
### SECCIÓN 2 — TASKS (CRUD básico)
###############################################

### 2.1 Listar tareas del usuario autenticado
GET {{host}}/tasks
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenTest}}

### 2.2 Crear una tarea
POST {{host}}/tasks
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenTest}}

{
    "category_id": 1,
    "title": "Comprar pan",
    "description": "Comprar pan para el desayuno",
    "status": "pending",
    "priority": "high",
    "due_date": "2026-12-31",
    "is_completed": false
}

### 2.3 Ver una tarea
GET {{host}}/tasks/1
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenTest}}

### 2.4 Actualizar una tarea
PUT {{host}}/tasks/1
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenTest}}

{
    "status": "completed",
    "is_completed": true
}

### 2.5 Eliminar una tarea
DELETE {{host}}/tasks/1
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenTest}}


