###############################################
### SECCIÓN 5 — SUBTASKS (CRUD anidado)
### Rutas: GET/POST /tasks/{task}/subtasks   |   GET/PUT/DELETE /subtasks/{subtask}
###############################################

### 5.1 Listar subtareas de una tarea
GET {{host}}/tasks/1/subtasks
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenTest}}

### 5.2 Crear una subtarea (anidada bajo task)
POST {{host}}/tasks/1/subtasks
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenTest}}

{
    "title": "Comprar leche",
    "is_completed": false
}

### 5.3 Ver una subtarea (ruta shallow)
GET {{host}}/subtasks/1
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenTest}}

### 5.4 Actualizar una subtarea
PUT {{host}}/subtasks/1
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenTest}}

{
    "title": "Comprar leche descremada",
    "is_completed": true
}

### 5.5 Eliminar una subtarea
DELETE {{host}}/subtasks/1
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenTest}}


